article.description: — Kevin Davis scored 16 points as Bethune-Cookman beat Idaho State 68-66 in overtime on Saturday night.
article.headline: Davis' 16 lead Bethune-Cookman past Idaho State 68-66 in OT
article.linkText: Davis' 16 lead Bethune-Cookman past Idaho State 68-66 in OT
article.story: CONWAY, Ark. -- — Kevin Davis scored 16 points as Bethune-Cookman beat Idaho State 68-66 in overtime on Saturday night. Davis shot 6 for 9, including 3 for 5 from beyond the arc for the Wildcats (3-3). Dylan Robertson scored 14 points and added seven rebounds. Zion Harmon shot 4 for 14 (1 for 3 from 3-point range) and 2 of 3 from the free throw line to finish with 11 points. Brock Mackenzie led the way for the Bengals (1-5) with 18 points. Miguel Tomley added 14 points and five assists and Daxton Carr had 12 points. ------ The Associated Press created this story using technology provided by Data Skrive and data from Sportradar.
